{"tid":890281,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"沙拿最新雕塑出爐","createTime":"2018-11-05T07:56:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T05:37:56.000Z","uid":31314,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"3501862136a556f05c847ad23875d84bcd233991","tid":890281,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T07:56:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DrM2UVhVYAA1mv1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDrM2UVhVYAA1mv1.jpg&h=6642e13d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.8T1NuA4.s744saRHph5ag--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjM0O2g9Nzc5/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/e40357c608d54ef2b84a18d601243a14\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F.8T1NuA4.s744saRHph5ag--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjM0O2g9Nzc5%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fe40357c608d54ef2b84a18d601243a14&h=2ff968d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一年前葡萄牙雕塑家艾曼紐山度士(Emanuel Santos) ，為球星基斯坦奴朗拿度（C朗）製作了一個銅像，可是製成品的樣子面容扭曲、笑容詭異，笑爆一眾球迷。埃及雕塑家阿拿（Mai Abdel Allah）為利物浦球星穆罕默德沙拿製作雕塑，可是出來的成品亦是「不似如期」，被網民指責與真人相距甚遠，笑指雕塑更像電影《寶貝智多星》的奸角Marv。<br />\n<br />\n為期4天的世界青年論壇正在埃及舉行，沙拿的雕塑就在論壇中展出。阿拿向埃及媒體透露，她花了一個月時間製作沙拿的雕塑，這是取材自沙拿打開雙臂的招牌入球慶祝動作。對於阿拿的傑作，網民似乎不太受落，認為該雕塑的C朗的詭異銅像醜十倍，「除了髮型相似，其他部份完全不似」。不過藝術的美醜從來都好主觀，還望球迷們不要過份批評阿拿吧！"},{"pid":"d35bdeecb38d72eb1409b73f062f09db7b1a7414","tid":890281,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T07:57:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cce4b2f76e93fe27e7e0443195f974dd2277287f","tid":890281,"uid":7854,"like":84,"dislike":0,"score":84,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T07:58:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/l0Iyl9368FDqN5K5G/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%